name: September → November
description:
Recycling the work that I've done.

Sometimes my work would be like on the left, sometimes would be like on the right. If I am ever consistent with the theme and presentation that I started, maybe my work would be still like on the left. But today, I have a lot of exploration and playful experimentation with my work just like the right one.

So what is consistency? Right now I just want to explore and play more before coming back to what I want to convey. Taking a detour with the creation method or a new theme to discover is a refreshing to do.
